t%20so%20did%20the%20boyfriend%2C%20who%20hung%20out%20with%20my%20daughter%20most%20weekends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20my%20daughter's%20first%20serious%20boyfriend%2C%20and%20the%20amount%20of%20time%20she%20spent%20wearing%20his%20hoodie%20seemed%20proportionate%20to%20the%20seriousness%20of%20their%20relationship.%20When%20the%20relationship%20ran%20its%20course%2C%20the%20hoodie%20and%20the%20boyfriend%20stopped%20showing%20up%20at%20our%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20daughter%20is%2017%20now%2C%20and%20a%20couple%20more%20hoodies%20haven't%20fared%20as%20well%20as%20the%20first%20two.%20One%20hoodie%20ended%20up%20underneath%20her%20bed%2C%20cut%20into%20little%20pieces.%20That%20hoodie%20belonged%20to%20a%20boyfriend%20who%20cheated%20on%20her.%20The%20phrase%20%26quot%3BHell%20hath%20no%20fury%20like%20a%20woman%20scorned%26quot%3B%20came%20to%20mind%20when%20I%20stumbled%20upon%20the%20shredded%20pieces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20another%20hoodie%20remains%20in%20a%20bag%20in%20our%20guest%20room.%20My%20daughter%20wanted%20to%20give%20it%20back%2C%20exchanging%20it%20for%20the%20hair%20scrunchies%20she'd%20given%20this%20particular%20ex%20to%20wear%20on%20his%20wrist%20(another%20symbol%20of%20Gen%20Z%20coupledom).%20But%20the%20pain%20of%20this%20breakup%20and%20perhaps%20the%20finality%20of%20returning%20the%20hoodie%20have%20hampered%20any%20chance%20of%20a%20meet-up.%20There's%20talk%20of%20donating%20this%20hoodie%20the%20next%20time%20we%20make%20a%20run%20to%20Goodwill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20no%20idea%20when%20the%20next%20hoodie%20will%20appear.%20It%20may%20be%20merely%20a%20phase%20or%20a%20fad.%20I%20hope%20eventually%20she%20finds%20one%20that%20is%20exciting%20yet%20comfortable%2C%20complements%20her%2C%20and%20lasts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-dating-girls-wear-boys-hoodies-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22publish