s.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHilton%20has%20been%20using%20Winnow%20to%C2%A0reduce%20waste%20at%20its%20breakfast%20buffets%20by%20serving%20smaller%20portions%20of%20croissants%2C%20fruit%2C%20and%20salmon.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EHotels%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-garbage-food-waste-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereducing%20how%20much%20food%20they%20waste%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20their%20breakfast%20buffets%20by%20installing%20AI-powered%20cameras%20above%20their%20kitchen%20trash%20cans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBritish%20company%20Winnow's%20hardware%20involves%20a%20scale%20that%20kitchens%20place%20a%20trash%20can%20on%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20screen%20with%20a%20motion-sensor%20camera.%20Its%20AI%20scans%20the%20items%20after%20they're%20placed%20in%20the%20trash%20%E2%80%94%20it%20can%20identify%20whether%20that%20was%20a%20bowl%20of%20carrot%20peelings%2C%20excess%20guacamole%2C%20or%20uneaten%20mashed%20potato%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20scale%20then%20records%20how%20much%20of%20that%20item%20was%20thrown%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChefs%20and%20restaurant%20managers%20can%20see%20this%20data%20in%20real%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Photos%20showing%20a%20display%20screen%20and%20a%20scale%20provided%20by%20the%20AI%20company%20Winnow%20for%20tracking%20food%20waste%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F668683ba1aace5b3ada47f04%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWinnow's%20hardware%20involves%20a%20scale%20and%20a%20screen%20with%20a%20motion-sensor%20camera.%20%3Cp%3EWinnow%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20system%20%26quot%3Bmakes%20it%20really%20easy%20for%20us%20to%20gather%20accurate%20data%20on%20what's%20being%20wasted%20in%20these%20kitchens%2C%26quot%3B%20Winnow%20cofounder%20Marc%20Zornes%20said%2C%20noting%20that%20the%20difficulty%20of%20collecting%20accurate%20recordings%20was%20the%20%26quot%3Bbiggest%20problem%26quot%3B%20many%20companies%20faced%20in%20tackling%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsell-by-best-before-dates-mean-nothing-create-food-waste-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efood%20waste%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20it's%20important%20that%20you%20make%20this%20process%20easy%20because%20kitchens%20are%20very%20busy%20places%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWinnow%20then%20uses%20this%20data%20to%20advise%20chefs%20on%20buying%20the%20right%20amount%20of%20ingredients%20and%20how%20to%20prepare%20them%20to%20minimize%20waste.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZornes%20said%20that%20Winnow's%20accuracy%20at%20identifying%20foods%20%26quot%3Bcan%20vary%20from%20site%20to%20site.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20it%20knows%20what%20it%20is%20outright%2C%20it%20identifies%20the%20product%2C%26quot%3B%20Zornes%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20it%20doesn't%20know%20what%20it%20is%20and%20it%20thinks%20it's%20a%20couple%20of%20options%2C%20it%20can%20present%20that%20to%20the%20user%2C%20and%20they%20can%20help%20the%20system%20get%20better%20over%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photo%20of%20a%20display%20screen%20from%20a%20Winnow%20scale.%20The%20screen%20shows%20a%20picture%20of%20french%20fries%20that%20have%20been%20placed%20in%20a%20trash%20can%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20weight%2C%20which%20is%20722g.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F668684121aace5b3ada47f0f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWinnow%20identifies%20what%20the%20food%20is%20and%20how%20much%20was%20thrown%20away.%3Cp%3EWinnow%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unep.org%2Fresources%2Fpublication%2Ffood-waste-index-report-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUnited%20Nations%20Environmental%20Program%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%2019%25%20of%20food%20available%20to%20consumers%20globally%20%E2%80%94%20or%20more%20than%201.1%20billion%20tons%20%E2%80%94%20was%20wasted%20in%202022.%20Of%20this%2C%20nearly%2030%25%20was%20wasted%20in%20the%20food%20service%20sector.%20Food%20loss%20in%20the%20supply%20chain%20and%20food%20waste%20generate%20almost%20five%20times%20the%20total%20greenhouse%20gas%20emissions%20from%20the%20aviation%20sector%2C%20per%20the%20UNEP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReducing%20food%20waste%20can%20boost%20a%20company's%20eco%20credentials%20%E2%80%94%20and%20cut%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWinnow's%20clients%20include%20hotels%2C%20cruise%20lines%2C%20universities%2C%20and%20food%20service%20companies%20that%20provide%20professional%20catering%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20it's%20not%20just%20back-of-house%20waste%20that%20they're%20tracking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20Hilton%20has%20been%20using%20Winnow%20to%20look%20at%20which%20items%20from%20its%20breakfast%20buffets%20are%20being%20wasted%20the%20most%2C%20Sebastian%20Nohse%2C%20Hilton%20EMEA's%20senior%20director%20of%20culinary%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBreakfast%20buffets%20create%20%26quot%3Ba%20really%20big%20chunk%20of%20waste%20that%20we%20in%20the%20hotel%20industry%20in%20general%20didn't%20really%20have%20clear%20insights%20about%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Hilton%20used%20data%20from%20Winnow%20to%20experiment%20with%20smaller%20croissants%2C%20fruit%2C%20and%20smoked%20salmon%20served%20in%20smaller%20portions%20for%20its%20breakfast%20buffets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20can%20remove%20choice%2C%20that%20will%20drive%20impact%2C%26quot%3B%20Nohse%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20can%20make%20the%20choice%20for%20the%20guests%20by%20providing%20a%20smaller%20croissant%20or%20a%20smaller%20doughnut%20or%20cutting%20the%20fruit%20in%20a%20different%20way%2C%20we%20can%20create%20positive%20impact%20without%20letting%20the%20guests%20make%20the%20choice%20but%20by%20creating%20impact%20by%20default.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20big%20portion%20sizes%20that%20are%20contributing%20to%20diners%20leaving%20food%20on%20their%20plates.%20Using%20Winnow%2C%20chefs%20can%20see%20which%20dishes%20aren't%20going%20down%20well%20with%20diners%2C%20Paul%20Fairhead%2C%20CEO%20of%20Guckenheimer%2C%20the%20food%20services%20arm%20of%20ISS%20which%20provides%20commercial%20catering%2C%20told%20BI.%20They%20can%20then%2C%20for%20example%2C%20consider%20whether%20the%20flavors%20of%20the%20dish%20weren't%20right%2C%20or%20check%20the%20pictures%20recorded%20by%20Winnow%20to%20see%20whether%20it%20just%20looked%20burned%20that%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWinnow%20declined%20to%20share%20specifics%20about%20how%20much%20its%20services%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHilton%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstories.hilton.com%2Femea%2Freleases%2Fhilton-green-breakfast-records-62-percent-reduction-in-food-waste-uae%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20in%20a%20%26quot%3BGreen%20Breakfast%26quot%3B%20pilot%20that%20involved%20making%20decisions%20based%20on%20Winnow%20data%20as%20well%20as%20introducing%20sustainable%20behavior%20%26quot%3Bnudges%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20cut%20food%20waste%20at%2013%20of%20its%20hotels%20in%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20over%20a%20four-month%20period%20in%202023%20by%2076%25%20for%20pre-consumer%2C%20or%20kitchen%2C%20waste%20and%20by%2055%25%20for%20post-consumer%20waste.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20wasted%20items%20included%20bread%20and%20pastry%2C%20white%20eggs%2C%20porridge%2C%20congee%2C%20sambar%2C%20shakshuka%20and%20baked%20beans%2C%20Hilton%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhotels-offices-kitchens-winnow-ai-tool-reduce-food-waste-costs-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720343522000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2F