0is%20on%20the%20run%2C%20was%20drunk%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20car%20belongs%20to%20Rajesh%20Shah%2C%20deputy%20leader%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Palghar%20district.%20The%20politician%20and%20his%20driver%20are%20now%20in%20police%20custody%20and%20a%20case%20has%20been%20registered.%20At%20the%20time%20of%20the%20accident%2C%20police%20said%2C%20the%20Sena%20leader's%20son%20and%20their%20driver%20were%20in%20the%20luxury%20car.%20Mihir%20Shah%20has%20switched%20off%20his%20phone%20and%20police%20are%20looking%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20police%20sources%2C%20Mihir%20Shah%20drank%20at%20a%20bar%20in%20Juhu%20last%20night.%20On%20his%20way%20home%2C%20he%20asked%20the%20driver%20to%20take%20him%20a%20long%20drive.%20The%20car%20came%20to%20Worli%20and%20then%20Mihir%20insisted%20that%20he%20would%20drive.%20Soon%20after%20he%20took%20the%20wheel%2C%20the%20speeding%20BMW%20hit%20a%20scooter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20scooter%20were%20Kaveri%20Nakva%20and%20her%20husband%20Pradik%20Nakva%2C%20residents%20of%20Worli's%20Koliwada%20area.%20The%20fish-seller%20couple%20went%20to%20Sassoon%20Dock%20daily%20to%20fetch%20fish.%20They%20were%20on%20their%20way%20back%2C%20when%20the%20BMW%20crashed%20into%20their%20two-wheeler.%20The%20two%20were%20thrown%20into%20the%20air%20and%20crashed%20on%20the%20bonnet%20of%20the%20SUV.%20As%20the%20car%20kept%20speeding%2C%20Kaveri%20Nakva%20was%20run%20over.%20The%20car%20fled%20the%20spot%20and%20the%20woman%20was%20rushed%20to%20a%20hospital%2C%20where%20she%20was%20declared%20dead.%20Her%20husband%2C%20Pradik%2C%20has%20suffered%20minor%20injuries.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police's%20investigation%20has%20also%20revealed%20attempts%20to%20destroy%20evidence.%20The%20car's%20windshield%20has%20a%20Shiv%20Sena%20sticker%2C%20which%20has%20been%20scratched%2C%20apparently%20to%20conceal%20the%20vehicle's%20link%20with%20the%20Sen