s%20iconic%20career%20in%2057%20seconds%20-%20watch%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720342968000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-111553267%2Cimgsize-75900.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Frelive-ms-dhonis-iconic-career-in-57-seconds-on-his-43rd-birthday-watch%2Farticleshow%2F111552909.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%20India's%202006%20tour%20of%20Pakistan%20onwards%2C%20Dhoni%20never%20looked%20back%20in%20his%20career%2C%20going%20on%20to%20become%20one%20of%20India's%20most%20iconic%20captains%2C%20who%20led%20the%20team%20to%20T20%20World%20Cup%20glory%20in%202007%2C%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20triumph%20in%202011%2C%20the%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy%20title%20in%202013%20and%20also%20playing%20a%20key%20role%20in%20making%20India%20No.%201%20in%20Test%20cricket%20under%20his%20captaincy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20European%20rival%20to%20HIMARS%20takes%20shape%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Contractors%20are%20developing%20a%20European%20rocket%20artillery%20system%20that%20could%20rival%20Lockheed%20Martin's%20HIMARS.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66859514268f62ba18a75582%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EContractors%20are%20developing%20a%20European%20rocket%20artillery%20system%20that%20could%20rival%20Lockheed%20Martin's%20HIMARS.%3Cp%3ESgt.%201st%20Class%20Timothy%20Cordeiro%2FUS%20Army%20National%20Guard%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EContractors%20are%20developing%20a%20rocket%20artillery%20system%20for%20Europe%20that%20could%20rival%20HIMARS.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20heavier%20EuroPULS%20could%20carry%20twice%20as%20many%20rockets.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHIMARS%20may%20be%20a%20victim%20of%20its%20popularity%2C%20as%20Lockheed%20Martin%20tries%20to%20meet%20surging%20demand.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEurope%20is%20building%20a%20multiple%20rocket%20launcher%20that%20resembles%20America's%20HIMARS%2C%20the%20ground-fired%20weapon%20that%20took%20on%20the%20precision%20strike%20missions%20that%20Ukraine's%20battered%20air%20force%20couldn't.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.knds.com%2Ffileadmin%2Fuser_upload%2Fcontent%2FNewsroom%2FPressAreas%2F2024_Eurosatory%2FEuroPULS%2FKNDS_DB_Ansicht_EuroPULS_EN.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EEuroPULS%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20a%20truck-mounted%20multiple%20rocket%20launcher%2C%20is%20a%20collaboration%20between%20Franco-German%20defense%20firm%20KNDS%20and%20Israel's%20Elbit%20Systems.%20It's%20based%20on%20Elbit's%20Precise%20and%20Universal%20Launching%20System%2C%20or%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Felbitsystems.com%2Fproduct%2Fpuls%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EPULS%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20which%20is%20fielded%20by%20the%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20and%20several%20European%20nations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20raises%20the%20question%20of%20whether%20EuroPULS%20will%20be%20a%20competitor%20to%20HIMARS%2C%20or%20High%20Mobility%20Artillery%20Rocket%20System%2C%20a%20decades-old%20launcher%20which%20made%20its%20name%20in%20the%20Ukraine%20war.%20Comparing%20EuroPULS%20to%20HIMARS%20reveals%20platforms%20that%20are%20similar%20in%20concept.%20EuroPULS%20is%20mounted%20on%20an%20eight-wheel%20truck%20chassis%2C%20while%20HIMARS%20uses%20a%20six-wheel%20vehicle.%20A%20KNDS%20fact%20sheet%20describes%20EuroPULS%20as%20being%2034-feet%20long%2C%20and%20weighing%2038%20tons%2C%20with%20a%20maximum%20road%20speed%20of%2055%20miles%20per%20hour.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20makes%20it%20much%20heavier%20than%20HIMARS%2C%20which%20has%20a%20combat-loaded%20weight%20of%2018%20tons.%20But%20a%20larger%20vehicle%20can%20carry%20more%20rockets.%20EuroPULS%20has%20two%20pods%2C%20which%20can%20fire%2012%20rockets%20in%2060%20seconds%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20munition.%20HIMARS%20has%20one%20pod%20that%20can%20fire%20six%20GMLRS%20rockets%20or%20one%20long-range%20ATACMS%20missile.%20The%20price%20for%20a%20EuroPULS%20system%20hasn't%20been%20disclosed.%20But%20a%20HIMARS%20launcher%20costs%20almost%20%245%20million%20apiece%2C%20according%20to%202024%20US%20Army%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.asafm.army.mil%2FPortals%2F72%2FDocuments%2FBudgetMaterial%2F2024%2FBase%2520Budget%2FProcurement%2FMissile%2520Procurement%2520Army.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebudget%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20figures%2C%20while%20a%20GMLRS%20rocket%20costs%20more%20than%20%24100%2C000%20each.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEuropean%20armies%20already%20field%20multiple%20launch%20rocket%20systems.%20Many%2C%20such%20as%20France's%20LRU%20and%20Germany's%20MARS%202%2C%20are%20based%20on%20the%20U.S.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.military.com%2Fequipment%2Fm270-multiple-launch-rocket-system%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EM270%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20a%20tracked%20mobile%20rocket%20launcher%2C%20and%20its%20Guided%20Multiple%20Launch%20Rocket%20System%20rockets.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22One%20HIMARS%20launcher%20can%20carry%20six%20GMLRS%20rockets%20or%20one%20longer-range%20ATACMS%20ballistic%20missile.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6685983c1f0c1cd6d7316de0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20HIMARS%20launcher%20can%20carry%20six%20GMLRS%20rockets%20or%20one%20longer-range%20ATACMS%20ballistic%20missile.%3Cp%3ESgt.%20Emely%20Gonzalez%2FUS%20Marine%20Corps%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEuroPULS%20broadens%20that%20menu%20of%20munitions.%20EuroPULS%20can%20fire%20a%20%26quot%3Bmix%20of%20European%20legacy%20and%20PULS%20rockets%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20KNDS.%20Elbit%20markets%20a%20variety%20of%20PULS%20pods.%20Pod%20choices%20include%2018%20Accular%20122-mm%20rockets%20with%20a%20range%20of%2022%20miles%2C%2010%20Accular%20160-mm%20rockets%20with%20a%20range%20of%2025%20miles%2C%20four%20EXTRA%20extended-range%20rockets%20that%20can%20reach%20out%20to%2093%20miles%2C%20and%20two%20Predator%20Hawk%20weapons%20with%20a%20range%20of%20186%20miles.%20Different%20pods%20can%20be%20mounted%20on%20the%20same%20vehicle.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat's%20also%20notable%20is%20that%20KNDS%20and%20Elbit%20are%20touting%20the%20ability%20of%20EuroPULS%20to%20fire%20all%20sorts%20of%20rockets.%20KNDS%20says%20the%20system%20is%20%26quot%3Badaptable%20to%20future%20missiles.%26quot%3B%20Elbit%20says%20EuroPULS%20%26quot%3Bwill%20form%20the%20basis%20for%20a%20modularly%20scalable%20and%20flexible%20artillery%20system%20that%20can%20be%20integrated%20to%20fire%20from%20any%20mobility%20platform%20with%20pinpoint%20accuracy%20and%20safety.%20The%20open%20EuroPULS%20concept%20does%20not%20exclude%20any%20provider%20of%20respective%20missiles%20from%20cooperation%20enabling%20EuroPULS%20users%20to%20employ%20those.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20suggests%20that%20EuroPULS%20could%20fire%20the%20GMLRS%20rockets%20launched%20by%20HIMARS.%20Except%20that%20HIMARS%20manufacturer%20Lockheed%20Martin%20has%20said%20that's%20not%20an%20option.%20%26quot%3BOur%20MLRS%20Family%20of%20Munitions%20cannot%20be%20integrated%20into%20the%20PULS%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Lockheed%20Martin%20executive%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.defensenews.com%2Fglobal%2Feurope%2F2024%2F06%2F18%2Fciting-missile-mismatch-lockheed-snarls-at-himars-challenge-in-europe%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EDefense%20News%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%26quot%3BIf%20Germany%20was%20to%20opt%20for%20PULS%20they%20could%20not%20gain%20access%20to%20our%20missiles.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhether%20EuroPULS%20could%20rival%20HIMARS%20is%20complicated.%20HIMARS%20does%20enjoy%20the%20immense%20advantage%20of%20its%20reputation%20in%20the%20Ukraine%20war%2C%20where%20it%20proved%20crucial%20in%20helping%20halt%20Russia's%20invasion%20in%202022.%20HIMARS%20rockets%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fukraine-says-it-has-destroyed-50-ammunition-depots-using-himars-war-with-russia-2022-07-25%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edestroyed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Russian%20ammunition%20depots%20and%20headquarters%2C%20disrupting%20logistics%20and%20command%20and%20control%2C%20and%20spurring%20Russian%20forces%20to%20move%20vital%20facilities%20deeper%20behind%20their%20lines.%20HIMARS%20and%20other%20GPS-guided%20weapons%20such%20as%20HIMARS%20have%20recently%20lost%20some%20of%20their%20luster%2C%20as%20extensive%20Russian%20jamming%20of%20GPS%20signals%20has%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussian-electronic-warfare-shows-us-needs-for-future-wars-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edegraded%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20accuracy%20of%20guidance%20systems.%20But%20for%20now%2C%20multiple%20rocket%20launchers%20are%20prized%20items.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20KNDS%20can%20use%20economic%20incentives%20as%20a%20carrot%2C%20or%20at%20least%20for%20European%20customers%3B%20Lockheed%20Martin%20produces%20its%20guided%20HIMARS%20rockets%20at%20plants%20in%20the%20US.%20The%20KNDS%20fact%20sheet%20stated%20that%20%26quot%3BEuropean%20production%20base%20of%20launcher%20and%20ammunition%20planned.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHIMARS%20is%20used%2C%20or%20has%20been%20ordered%2C%20by%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20nations.%20But%20Elbit's%20PULS%20has%20already%20had%20some%20success%20in%20Europe%2C%20with%20the%20Netherlands%20and%20Denmark%20purchasing%20it%2C%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.janes.com%2Fosint-insights%2Fdefence-news%2Fweapons%2Ffuture-artillery-2024-germany-plans-to-procure-puls-mrls%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EGermany%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20planning%20to%20buy%20five%20to%20replace%20MARS%202%20launchers%20sent%20to%20Ukraine%2C%20and%20possibly%20as%20many%20as%2089.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20some%20extent%2C%20HIMARS%20may%20be%20a%20victim%20of%20its%20popularity%2C%20with%20questions%20about%20whether%20Lockheed%20Martin%20can%20meet%20surging%20demand%20for%20the%20launchers%20and%20rockets%2C%20though%20the%20company%20plans%20to%20boost%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thedefensepost.com%2F2024%2F02%2F19%2Flockheed-himars-production-60%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emanufacturing%20capacity%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Ukraine%20for%20example%20has%20ordered%20new%20HIMARS%20launchers%20and%20the%20US%20Defense%20Department%20is%20replacing%20the%20launchers%20and%20missiles%20from%20its%20arsenal%20that%20it%20provided%20to%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BDemand%20for%20such%20military%20capabilities%20risks%20outstripping%20supply%2C%20given%20limitations%20on%20how%20quickly%20industrial%20production%20capacity%20can%20be%20ramped%20up%20and%20given%20the%20need%20to%20also%20backfill%20or%20provide%20systems%20for%20Ukraine%2C%26quot%3B%20James%20Black%2C%20assistant%20director%20for%20defense%20at%20the%20RAND%20Europe%20think%20tank%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20also%20industrial%20policy%20and%20security%20of%20supply%20questions%20at%20play%2C%20with%20many%20nations%20hoping%20to%20assure%20access%20to%20production%20lines%20and%20munitions%20in%20times%20of%20crisis%20or%20war%2C%20and%20with%20many%20countries%20hoping%20to%20secure%20lucrative%20domestic%20or%20export%20contracts.%20Collectively%2C%20such%20trends%20are%20prompting%20some%20militaries%20to%20consider%20possible%20alternatives%20to%20the%20US%20HIMARS%20system%2C%20though%20certainly%20that%20remains%20a%20major%20player%20in%20this%20competition%20for%20contracts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EMichael%20Peck%20is%20a%20defense%20writer%20whose%20work%20has%20appeared%20in%20Forbes%2C%20Defense%20News%2C%20Foreign%20Policy%20magazine%2C%20and%20other%20publications.%20He%20holds%20an%20MA%20in%20political%20science%20from%20Rutgers%20Univ.%20Follow%20him%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitter.com%2F%40mipeck1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3ETwitter%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fmipeck%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3ELinkedIn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-european-europuls-rocket-launcher-could-rival-himars-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720342802000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F668595de1aace5b3ada44e33%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-european-europuls-rocket-launcher-could-rival-himars-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20heavy%2C%20truck-mounted%20EuroPULS%20launcher%20can%20carry%20twice%20as%20many%20rockets%20as%20Lockheed%20Martin's%20HIMARS.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Michael%20Peck)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-european-europuls-rocket-launcher-could-rival-himars-2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Here's%20How%20Long%20It%20May%20Take%20For%20Sensex%20To%20Reach%201%20Lakh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Frm7qjlog_bse-sensex_625x300_04_July_24.jpeg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20markets%20are%20soaring%20to%20new%20heights.%20The%20Sensex%20closed%20at%2080%2C049.67%20on%20July%204%20rebounding%20strongly%20after%20recent%20uncertainty%20surrounding%20the%20elections.%20The%20index%20has%20surpassed%20year-end%20targets%20set%20by%20numerous%20brokerage%20firms.%20Leading%20investors%20project%20the%20Sensex%20to%20potentially%20reach%20the%201%20lakh%20mark%20within%20the%20next%20three%20to%20five%20years.%20Billionaire%20investor%20Mark%20Mobius%20expressed%20confidence%20in%20India's%20bullish%20market%2C%20suggesting%20the%20Sensex%20could%20even%20breach%201%20lakh%20before%20the%20end%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi's%20third%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sensex%20jumped%20from%2070%2C000%20to%2080%2C000%20in%20less%20than%20seven%20months.%20Since%20its%20inception%20at%20100%20in%20April%201979%2C%20it%20has%20grown%20by%20an%20impressive%2015.9%25%20annually%2C%20expanding%20800-fold.%20Doubling%20from%201%2C000%20to%202%2C000%20points%20took%201.48%20years%2C%20and%20further%20to%204%2C000%20points%20in%20just%200.21%20years%20by%20March%201992.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20then%20took%206.33%20years%20to%20double%20from%205%2C000%20to%2010%2C000%20points%20in%20February%202006.%20Subsequently%2C%20it%20doubled%20again%20to%2020%2C000%20points%20in%201.84%20years%2C%20and%20to%2040%2C000%20points%20in%2011.45%20years%20by%20May%202019.%20From%2040%2C000%20to%2080%2C000%2C%20the%20journey%20spanned%20five%20years%20and%201.5%20months.%20On%20an%20average%2C%20the%20benchmark%20index%20doubled%20in%20a%20little%20over%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fs69o6ku8_sensex-1_625x300_07_July_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20historical%20CAGR%20of%2016%25%2C%20achieving%20the%201%20lakh%20milestone%20by%20December%202025%20seems%20optimistic%20yet%20feasible%2C%20if%20sustained%20growth%20continues.%20However%2C%20maintaining%20such%20high%20returns%20from%20a%20higher%20base%20could%20prove%20challenging.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20Sensex%20more%20than%20tripling%20since%20its%20March%202020%20lows%2C%20optimism%20remains%20tempered%20by%20potential%20market%20volatility%20ahead.%20Along%20the%20path%20to%201%20lakh%2C%20three%20key%20indicators%20emerge%20as%20crucial%3A%3Cbr%3E%5CnHistorical%20Doubling%20Periods%3A%20While%20past%20performance%20isn't%20indicative%20of%20future%20outcomes%2C%20Sensex's%20quickest%20doubling%20-%20from%202%2C000%20to%204%2C000%20points%20-%20took%20just%202.5%20months%20in%201992.%20Conversely%2C%20its%20longest%20doubling%20period%20was%20from%202007%20to%202019%2C%20taking%20about%2011.5%20years%20to%20jump%20from%2020%2C000%20to%2040%2C000%20points.%20The%20index%20reached%2050%2C000%20points%20in%20January%202021%2C%20suggesting%20a%20historical%20doubling%20period%20of%20approximately%20five%20years%2C%20potentially%20placing%201%20lakh%20within%20reach%20by%20January%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESensex%20Returns%20And%20GDP%20Growth%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20nominal%20terms%20(before%20adjusting%20for%20inflation)%2C%20Sensex%20has%20delivered%20a%20compounded%20annual%20growth%20rate%20of%20close%20to%2016%25%20since%20its%20inception%20in%201979%2C%20over%20the%20past%2045%20years.%20This%20growth%20rate%20is%20comparable%20to%20the%20nominal%20GDP%20growth%20of%20the%20Indian%20economy%20over%20the%20same%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20economy%20is%20projected%20to%20grow%20at%206.5%25-7%25%20over%20the%20next%20three%20years%20as%20India%20becomes%20the%20third-largest%20economy.%20Assuming%20a%20nominal%20return%20of%207%25%20annually%20for%20the%20next%20three%20and%20a%20half%20years%2C%20the%20Sensex%20could%20reach%20a%20value%20of%20around%201%20lakh%20by%20December%202027.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EMarket%20Cap%20to%20GDP%20Ratio%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20March%202024%2C%20the%20market%20cap%20to%20GDP%20ratio%20stood%20at%20135%25.%20Over%20the%20past%2020%20years%2C%20the%20average%20ratio%20has%20been%20above%2083%25%2C%20suggesting%20that%20current%20market%20valuations%20may%20be%20relatively%20high%20compared%20to%20the%2020-year%20historical%20average.%20Interestingly%2C%20the%20Indian%20stock%20market%20hit%20a%20bottom%20around%20the%20same%20ratio%20in%202020%20following%20COVID-19%2C%20as%20it%20did%20in%20March%202009%20after%20the%20Global%20Financial%20Crisis%2C%20at%2053%25-55%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EImplications%20Of%20A%20Market%20Correction%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20analysts%20believe%20the%20markets%20are%20overheated%2C%20citing%20the%20high%20market%20cap%20to%20GDP%20ratio%2C%20and%20anticipate%20an%20imminent%20correction.%20The%20exact%20timing%20and%20extent%20of%20this%20correction%20are%20difficult%20to%20predict%20accurately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20there%20is%20a%20correction%20of%2010%25%20from%20current%20levels%2C%20achieving%20an%20annual%20return%20of%2012%25%20would%20be%20necessary%20to%20reach%20the%20target%20of%201%20lakh%20by%202027.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20a%2020%25%20correction%2C%20a%20return%20of%2016%25%20per%20year%20would%20be%20required.%20Both%2012%25%20and%2016%25%20annual%20returns%20are%20considered%20ambitious%20given%20the%20large%20base%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20a%20correction%20of%2010%25-20%25%20occurs%2C%20the%201%20lakh%20milestone%20might%20be%20achieved%20by%202029%2C%20aligning%20with%20the%20conclusion%20of%20Modi's%20third%20term.%20However%2C%20if%20no%20correction%20occurs%2C%20Sensex%20appears%20to%20be%20on%20track%20to%20reach%20the%20target%20by%202027.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720342620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Frm7qjlog_bse-sensex_625x300_04_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fheres-how-long-it-may-take-for-sensex-to-reach-1-lakh-6052624%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22If%20a%20correction%20of%2010%25-20%25%20occurs%2C%20the%201%20lakh%20milestone%20might%20be%20achieved%20by%202029%2C%20aligning%20with%20the%20conclusion%20of%20Modi's%20third%20term.%20However%2C%20if%20no%20correction%20occurs%2C%20Sensex%20appears%20to%20be%20on%20track%20to%20reach%20the%20target%20by%202027.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fheres-how-long-it-may-take-for-sensex-to-reach-1-lakh-6052624%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fheres-how-long-it-may-take-for-sensex-to-reach-1-lakh-6052624%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fheres-how-long-it-may-take-for-sensex-to-reach-1-lakh-6052624%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Phone%20Data%20Bought%20For%20Rs%202%2C500%20Used%20For%20Multi-Crore%20Scam%20Running%20In%20Noida%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPhone%20data%20bought%20online%20with%20just%20Rs%202%2C500%20was%20used%20to%20defraud%20hundreds%20of%20people%20in%20a%20multi-crore%20loan%20scam%20running%20from%20a%20fake%20call%20centre%20in%20Noida%2C%20police%20said.%20Eleven%20people%2C%20including%20nine%20women%2C%20were%20arrested%20for%20selling%20fake%20insurance%20policies%20and%20loans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20call%20centre%2C%20run%20by%20two%20former%20life%20insurance%20policy%20agents%2C%20operated%20from%20the%20fourth%20floor%20of%20a%20building%20in%20Noida's%20Sector%2051%20market%20for%20over%20a%20year.%20Police%20said%20the%20gang%20lured%20people%20from%20outside%20Delhi-NCR%20by%20promising%20high%20returns%20on%20loans%20and%20insurance%20policies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scam's%20masterminds%2C%20Ashish%20and%20Jitendra%2C%20hired%20nine%20women%20to%20act%20as%20call%20centre%20executives%20who%20would%20call%20people%20and%20sell%20them%20these%20policies.%20The%20gang%20bought%20SIM%20cards%20through%20fake%20Aadhaar%20cards%20bought%20illegally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20SIM%20cards%20were%20used%20to%20hide%20their%20identities%20while%20targeting%20unsuspecting%20victims.%20The%20organisation%20functioned%20based%20on%20commission%20--%20the%20more%20people%20you%20lure%20in%2C%20the%20more%20money%20you%20get.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20money%20from%20the%20victims%20of%20the%20scam%20was%20received%20in%20a%20Punjab%20National%20Bank%20account%20that%20was%20rented%20for%20Rs%2010%2C00%20a%20month%20from%20a%20man%20named%20Arvind%20in%20Karnataka.%20Both%20Ashish%20and%20Jitendra%20would%20then%20use%20debit%20cards%20to%20withdraw%20the%20money%20in%20Noida.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20police%20raid%2C%20a%20black%20diary%20used%20by%20Ashish%20was%20found.%20The%20diary%20detailed%20every%20financial%20transaction%20in%20the%20year-long%20scam%20which%20generated%20crores%20of%20rupees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20was%20busted%20on%20Friday%20in%20a%20joint%20operation%20by%20the%20Crime%20Response%20Team%20(CRT)%20and%20the%20local%20Sector%2049%20police%20station%20officials%2C%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20(DCP)%20Shakti%20Mohan%20Avasthy%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5CnA%20case%20for%20a%20similar%20scam%20was%20filed%20against%20then%20in%20Ranchi%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAshish%20and%20Jitendra%20started%20this%20fraudulent%20activity%20after%20working%20for%20SBI%20Life%20Insurance%20in%202019.%20They%20bought%20data%20of%20about%2010%2C000%20people%20from%20India%20Mart%20for%20Rs%202%2C500%20and%20began%20calling%20people%20across%20India%2C%20defrauding%20them%20under%20the%20pretence%20of%20offering%20loans%20and%20insurance%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20identified%20those%20arrested%20as%20key%20accused%20Ashish%20Kumar%20alias%20Amit%20and%20Jitendra%20Verma%20alias%20Abhishek.%20The%20nine%20women%20arrested%20are%20Nisha%20alias%20Sneha%2C%20Reju%20alias%20Divya%2C%20Lovely%20Yadav%20alias%20Sweta%2C%20Poonam%20alias%20Pooja%2C%20Aarti%20Kumari%20alias%20Ananya%2C%20Kajal%20Kumari%20alias%20Surti%2C%20Sarita%20alias%20Suman%2C%20Babita%20Patel%20alias%20Mahi%2C%20and%20Garima%20Chauhan%20alias%20Sonia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20First%20Information%20Report%20(FIR)%20has%20been%20filed%20in%20the%20case%20under%20provisions%20of%20the%20newly-enacted%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%20and%20all%20the%20accused%20have%20been%20sent%20to%20judicial%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720342620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Fgabies5_call-centre-generic_625x300_01_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fcities%2Fhow-fake-noida-call-centre-run-by-ex-insurance-agents-scammed-hundreds-6051283%22%2C%22s