of%20106%20per%20cent%20in%20July.%20Kukumseri%20in%20Lahaul%20and%20Spiti%20recorded%20the%20lowest%20night%20temperature%20at%2011.6%20degrees%20Celsius%20while%20Chamba%20was%20the%20hottest%20during%20the%20day%20with%20a%20maximum%20temperature%20of%2034.1%20degrees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20neighbouring%20Utttarakhand%2C%20the%20India%20Meteorological%20Department%20(IMD)%20has%20predicted%20heavy%20to%20extremely%20heavy%20rain%20over%20the%20next%20few%20days.%20%26quot%3BThunderstorms%20with%20lightning%20and%20intense%20to%20very%20intense%20spells%20are%20likely%20on%20July%208-9%20in%20the%20hills%20and%20plains%20of%20the%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20forecast%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChamoli%2C%20Rudraprayag%2C%20and%20Pauri%20districts%20of%20Uttarakhand%20have%20been%20the%20worst%20affected.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720331400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F6nn9rdao_shimla-landslide_625x300_07_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvideo-massive-landslide-in-himachal-pradeshs-shimla-after-heavy-rain-6051626%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20major%20landslide%20blocked%20a%20road%20on%20National%20Highway%20707%20near%20Shimla's%20Rohana%20after%20heavy%20rains%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh.%20The%20highway%2C%20which%20connects%20Hatkoti%20and%20Paonta%20Sahib%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20has%20been%20closed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvideo-massive-landslide-in-himachal-pradeshs-shimla-after-heavy-rain-6051626%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvideo-massive-landslide-in-himachal-pradeshs-shimla-after-heavy-rain-6051626%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvideo-massive-landslide-in-himachal-pradeshs-shimla-after-heavy-rain-6051626%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22