B%20would%20prompt%20him%20to%20even%20consider%20ending%20his%20bid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20the%20president%2C%2081%2C%20avoided%20a%20significant%20gaffe%20like%20the%20ones%20that%20bedeviled%20his%20disjointed%20debate%20performance%2C%20the%2022-minute%20prime-time%20interview%20with%20anchor%20George%20Stephanopoulos%20was%20unlikely%20to%20assuage%20concerns%20among%20the%20voters%2C%20donors%2C%20and%20Democratic%20officials%20who%20have%20spent%20the%20past%20week%20in%20a%20panic%20that%20he%20not%20only%20would%20fail%20to%20defeat%20his%20Republican%20opponent%2C%20but%20would%20not%20be%20able%20to%20serve%20another%20four%20years%20even%20if%20he%20managed%20reelection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'll%20feel%20as%20long%20as%20I%20gave%20it%20my%20all%20and%20I%20did%20the%20goodest%20job%20as%20I%20know%20I%20can%20do%2C%20that's%20what%20this%20is%20about%2C%26quot%3B%20Biden%20said%20when%20asked%20how%20he%20will%20feel%20in%20January%20if%20Trump%20wins%20the%20election%2C%20a%20nightmare%20scenario%20for%20Democrats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden's%20posture%20is%20perhaps%20the%20only%20strategy%20available%20for%20a%20candidate%20who%20is%20determined%20to%20continue%20his%20bid%20to%20win%20a%20second%20term.%20After%20Biden%20unveiled%20a%20revamped%20stump%20speech%20earlier%20Friday%20that%20acknowledged%20his%20age%20and%20more%20forcefully%20attacked%20Trump%2C%20his%20campaign%20indicated%20he%20plans%20to%20soldier%20on%20with%20more%20events%20Sunday%20in%20battleground%20Pennsylvania%20and%20beyond.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMultiple%20polls%20released%20following%20the%20debate%20showed%20Biden%20losing%20ground%20to%20Trump%2C%20with%20several%20showing%20him%20trailing%20by%206%20percentage%20points.%20The%20share%20of%20voters%20in%20a%20New%20York%20Times%2FSiena%20College%20poll%20who%20believe%20he%20is%20too%20old%20to%20be%20president%20grew%20to%2074%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDismisses%20Polls%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20if%20he%20believes%20he%20is%20not%20behind%2C%20however%2C%20Biden%20said%20%26quot%3Ball%20the%20pollsters%20I%20talk%20to%20tell%20me%20it's%20a%20tossup.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20Democratic%20donor%2C%20who%20requested%20anonymity%20to%20speak%20candidly%2C%20said%20they%20are%20angry%20at%20those%20in%20Biden's%20orbit%20for%20not%20encouraging%20him%20to%20step%20down%2C%20calling%20the%20continued%20campaign%20delusional%20and%20selfish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20is%20dangerously%20out-of-touch%20with%20the%20concerns%20people%20have%26quot%3B%20David%20Axelrod%2C%20a%20former%20Obama%20White%20House%20adviser%20who%20has%20been%20critical%20of%20Biden%2C%20posted%20on%20X%20after%20the%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20Biden's%20ABC%20appearance%2C%20Illinois%20Representative%20Mike%20Quigley%20joined%20a%20group%20of%20more%20than%20half%20a%20dozen%20House%20Democrats%20who%20have%20either%20explicitly%20called%20on%20the%20president%20to%20drop%20out%2C%20or%20said%20they%20believe%20he%20would%20lose%20to%20Trump%20in%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20acknowledged%20Senator%20Mark%20Warner%2C%20a%20prominent%20Democrat%20from%20Virginia%2C%20was%20looking%20to%20rally%20other%20lawmakers%20to%20pressure%20him%20to%20drop%20out.%20The%20president%20said%20he%20had%20heard%20from%20others%20that%20he%20should%20remain%20in%20the%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMark%20and%20I%20have%20a%20different%20perspective%2C%26quot%3B%20Biden%20told%20Stephanopoulos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20Lord%20Almighty%20came%20down%20and%20said%2C%20'Joe%2C%20get%20out%20of%20the%20race%2C'%20I'd%20get%20out%20of%20the%20race.%20The%20Lord%20Almighty's%20not%20coming%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20president%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Wasn't%20In%20Control'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20chalked%20up%20his%20poor%20debate%20performance%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bbad%20episode%26quot%3B%20brought%20on%20by%20a%20severe%20cold%20and%20that%20there%20was%20%26quot%3Bno%20indication%20of%20any%20serious%20condition.%26quot%3B%20Asked%20when%20he%20realized%20that%20he%20was%20having%20a%20bad%20night%2C%20Biden%20suggested%20that%20at%20one%20point%20he%20had%20been%20distracted%20by%20Trump%20shouting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20realized%20that%20I%20just%20wasn't%20in%20control%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20of%20that%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20he%20had%20watched%20his%20debate%20performance%2C%20which%20alarmed%20Democratic%20allies%2C%20Biden%20said%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20I%20did%2C%20no.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20interview%20came%20during%20a%20trip%20to%20Wisconsin%20in%20which%20Biden%20flatly%20declared%20he%20was%20not%20considering%20dropping%20out%20of%20the%20race.%20He%20said%20those%20looking%20to%20pressure%20him%20were%20disrespecting%20the%20will%20of%20Democratic%20primary%20voters%2C%20and%20that%20he%20still%20believed%20he%20represented%20the%20best%20chance%20for%20Democrats%20of%20defeating%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20will%20be%20put%20to%20the%20test%20over%20the%20coming%20week%20in%20the%20face%20of%20growing%20concern%20from%20Democratic%20lawmakers%20and%20donors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20his%20trip%20to%20Pennsylvania%2C%20Biden%20hosts%20NATO%20leaders%20starting%20Tuesday%20at%20a%20summit%20in%20Washington.%20The%20president's%20ramped-up%20schedule%20is%20a%20response%20to%20panicked%20Democrats%20who%20have%20demanded%20he%20do%20more%20to%20prove%20to%20voters%20he%20is%20capable%20of%20serving%20another%20four%20years%20in%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20some%20Democrats%20remain%20wary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20met%20Wednesday%20behind%20closed%20doors%20with%20more%20than%2020%20Democratic%20governors%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20stem%20the%20crisis%20engulfing%20his%20presidency%2C%20telling%20them%20he%20is%20%26quot%3Bin%20it%20to%20win%20it.%26quot%3B%20He%20received%20public%20votes%20of%20confidence%20from%20several%20of%20them%2C%20including%20California's%20Gavin%20Newsom%20and%20Michigan's%20Gretchen%20Whitmer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20privately%2C%20the%20governors%20had%20tough%20questions%20for%20the%20president%20and%20he%20acknowledged%20that%20he%20needs%20to%20get%20more%20sleep%20going%20forward%2C%20according%20to%20a%20person%20familiar%20with%20the%20discussion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20participants%2C%20Massachusetts%20Governor%20Maura%20Healey%2C%20issued%20a%20statement%20Friday%20that%20stopped%20short%20of%20calling%20on%20Biden%20to%20drop%20out%20but%20appeared%20to%20push%20him%20to%20at%20least%20consider%20the%20possibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20urge%20him%20to%20listen%20to%20the%20American%20people%20and%20carefully%20evaluate%20whether%20he%20remains%20our%20best%20hope%20to%20defeat%20Donald%20Trump%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720317480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fo44j52qo_joe-biden_625x300_03_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-elections-donald-trump-joe-biden-invokes-lord-almighty-amid-calls-to-end-reelection-bid-6050959%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Joe%20Biden%20on%20Friday%20in%20an%20ABC%20News%20interview%20refused%20to%20commit%20to%20an%20independent%20medical%20exam%20to%20reassure%20the%20public%20of%20his%20mental%20fitness%2C%20even%20as%20he%20insisted%20he%20has%20the%20stamina%20to%20serve%20another%20four%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-elections-donald-trump-jo