CWe%20were%20stuck%20in%20China%20and%20had%20to%20wear%20PPE%20kits%2C%20coveralls%2C%20and%20masks.%20Life%20was%20hell%20as%20we%20had%20no%20flights%20back%20home.%20It%20was%20mental%20torture%20for%20all%20of%20us%20on%20board%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20this%2C%20being%20on%20sea%20definitely%20comes%20with%20challenges%2C%20as%20you%20have%20to%20work%20in%20the%20engine%20room%20in%2050-55%20centigrade%20temperatures!%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20especially%20challenging%20during%20your%20%E2%80%98periods%E2%80%99.%20But%20I%20believe%20that%20you%20have%20to%20work%20hard%20to%20reach%20the%20top.%20A%20seafarer%20is%20a%20seafarer%2C%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20gender%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20ability%20to%20rise%20above%20challenges%20led%20to%20rapid%20advancement%20in%20her%20career%2C%20as%20she%20progressed%20from%20ETO%20to%20senior%20ETO%20to%20electrical%20superintendent%20in%20just%20four%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98At%20just%2026%2C%20I%20handled%2064%20vessels%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20the%20first%20lady%20superintendent%20in%20Maersk%20and%20also%20the%20youngest%20one%20at%2026.%20I%20handled%2064%20vessels%20and%20provided%20electrical%20support%20and%20remote%20resolution.%20I%20was%20responsible%20for%20various%20projects%20such%20as%20LED%20lights%20in%20vessels%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCr-xcm0tco4%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCr-xcm0tco4%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2