20we%20were%20able%20to%20design%20an%20innovative%20model%20house.%20This%20will%20inspire%20people%20to%20make%20homes%20from%20plastic.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHouse%20made%20from%20chips%20packets%2C%20broken%20mugs%20and%20bottles%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20early%20this%20year%2C%20Dr%20Balmukund%20segregated%20and%20collected%20plastic%20waste%20like%20chips%20packets%2C%20shampoo%20bottles%2C%20and%20broken%20plastic%20mugs%20from%20dumping%20grounds%20in%20the%20city.%20After%20drying%20them%20naturally%2C%20he%20shredded%20them%20into%20pellets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fplastic-house-2-1720100452.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22It%E2%80%99s%20completely%20made%20using%20plastic%20%E2%80%94%20right%20from%20the%20floor%20tiles%2C%20doors%2C%20and%20walls%20to%20stairs%20and%20ceiling!%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fplastic-house-2-1720100452.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fplastic-house-2-1720100452-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fplastic-house-2-1720100452-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fplastic-house-2-1720100452-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fplastic-house-2-1720100452-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355661%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20house%20is%20completely%20made%20using%20plastic%20%E2%80%94%20right%20from%20the%20floor%20tiles%2C%20doors%2C%20and%20walls%20to%20the%20stairs%20and%20roof!%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20pellets%20are%20melted%20into%20a%20semi-solid%20substance%20through%20an%20extruder.%20This%20substance%20can%20thus%20be%20moulded%20into%20any%20shape%2C%20like%20doors%2C%20legs%20of%20a%20bench%2C%20tiles%2C%20etc.%20Thereafter%2C%20it%20is%20passed%20through%20a%20chiller%20and%20later%20on%2C%20polished%20and%20coloured%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20Dr%20Balmukund%20three%20months%20to%20construct%20the%20plastic%20house.%20He%20has%20carved%20designs%20on%20the%20doors%20and%20beds%20in%20the%20house%20to%20give%20it%20a%20wooden%20look.%20%E2%80%9CSeeing%20the%20house%2C%20nobody%20can%20guess%20it%20is%20completely%20made%20of%20plastic%20waste.%20We%20have%20also%20used%20an%20additional%202.5%20tonnes%20of%20steel%20for%20rigid%20support%20and%20framework%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20more%20about%20the%20features%20of%20the%20house%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20house%20can%20be%20used%20in%20areas%20which%20are%20prone%20to%20electric%20shock%20or%20extreme%20hot%20and%20cold.%20As%20it%20is%20made%20from%20plastic%2C%20it%20provides%20insulation%20from%20outside%20weather.%20The%20house%20is%20comparatively%20three%20to%20four%20degrees%20cooler%20than%20outside%20temperatures%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCompared%20to%20a%20cement%20home%2C%20you%20do%20not%20require%20any%20water%20to%20construct%20a%20plastic%20house.%20Also%2C%20in%20reinforced%20concrete%2C%20percolation%20and%20cracks%20will%20eventually%20occur%2C%20but%20in%20a%20plastic%20home%2C%20there%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20any%20cracks.%20The%20reinforced%20cemented%20structures%20require%20maintenance%20in%2020%20to%2025%20years%20but%20no%20such%20maintenance%20is%20needed%20in%20structures%20made%20of%20plastic%2C%20which%20can%20last%20for%20decades%2C%20even%20after%20your%20lifetime%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%