.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20looked%20for%20the%20perfect%20land%20for%20nearly%20a%20decade%20before%20finding%20this%20one.%20His%20vision%20is%20a%20lush%20green%20tropical%20forest%20today.%20The%20Greenara%20Homestay%20is%20a%20part%20of%20that%20vision%2C%E2%80%9D%20Haneena%20P%20A%2C%20his%20daughter%20who%20manages%20the%20homestay%20with%20him%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocated%20amidst%20the%20tropical%20forest%20that%20Mustafa%20planted%20in%20Kerala%E2%80%99s%20Karipur%2C%20surrounding%20it%20with%20seven%20water%20bodies%2C%20the%20homestay%20is%20the%20natural%20getaway%20of%20your%20dreams.%20The%20property%20with%20three%20stay%20options%20is%20made%20with%20natural%20materials%20like%20mud%2C%20straw%20and%20wood%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F289271%2Fkerala-couple-build-zero-cement-eco-friendly-home-with-recycled-material-around-natural-rocks%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eusing%20zero%20cement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20journey%20back%20to%20his%20childhood%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20on%20a%20farm%2C%20Mustafa%20always%20missed%20living%20in%20the%20lush%2C%20green%20area.%20The%20inspiration%20behind%20the%20project%20was%20partly%20because%20he%20wanted%20to%20relive%20his%20childhood.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20development%20in%20the%20state%20of%20Kerala%2C%20he%20felt%20like%20the%20green%20cover%20was%20reducing%20massively.%20In%20a%20bid%20to%20do%20his%20part%20in%20bringing%20it%20back%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20undertake%20the%20project.%20It%20was%20a%20friend%20who%20alerted%20him%20of%20the%20land%20where%20Greenara%20now%20stands.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%