0tree%20in%20a%20big%20container%20or%20a%20grow%20bag%20on%20the%20terrace%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhijeet%20says%20that%20jackfruit%20can%20be%20planted%20from%20seeds%2C%20cuttings%20or%20saplings%20bought%20from%20the%20nursery.%20It%20is%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20when%20planted%20from%20seeds%2C%20it%20may%20take%20about%20seven%20years%20for%20it%20to%20bear%20fruit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20if%20you%20bring%20a%20grafted%20plant%20from%20the%20nursery%20and%20plant%20it%2C%20you%20will%20start%20getting%20fruits%20in%20about%20three%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fjackfruit-1-1719926465.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22It%20takes%20about%20a%20month%20and%20a%20half%20before%20your%20plant%20starts%20growing.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fjackfruit-1-1719926465.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fjackfruit-1-1719926465-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fjackfruit-1-1719926465-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fjackfruit-1-1719926465-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fjackfruit-1-1719926465-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355176%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIt%20takes%20about%20a%20month%20and%20a%20half%20before%20your%20plant%20starts%20growing.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHe%20shares%2010%20tips%20to%20grow%20jackfruit%20on%20the%20terrace%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%