ries%20and%20she%20says%20recovery%20is%20still%20on%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Sakshi%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20this%20challenging%20scene%20that%20Sakshi%20announced%20her%20decision%20to%20continue%20her%20MBBS%20studies.%20Everyone%20was%20taken%20aback%2C%20particularly%20her%20friends%2C%20colleagues%20and%20professors%2C%20she%20says%2C%20who%20thought%20she%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20resume%20studies%20so%20quickly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20hindsight%2C%20she%20feels%20it%20was%20the%20right%20decision.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20accelerated%20my%20recovery%20process%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20being%20unable%20to%20hold%20a%20pen%20to%20securing%20a%20distinction%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGetting%20Sakshi%20on%20her%20feet%20took%20a%20village.%20Everyone%20played%20their%20part%20well%2C%20she%20notes%2C%20adding%20that%20her%20dad%20formed%20a%20core%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F311674%2Fkolkata-samriddhi-malhotra-transforming-life-after-abusive-marriage-yoga-breathwork-goa%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eher%20support%20system%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20would%20set%20mini%20goals%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESakshi%20goes%20on%20to%20share%20an%20anecdote%20of%20the%20time%20she%20had%20just%20started%20to%20use%20the%20walker.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20very%20painful.%20I%20could%20hardly%20go%20out%20of%20the%20room%20before%20wanting%20to%20give%20up%20and%20get%20back%20to%20bed.%20But%20my%20dad%20made%20a%20rule%20that%20as%20soon%20as%20I%20felt%20like%20giving%20up%2C%20I%20would%20take%20five%20more%20steps%20and%20then%20make%20a%20U-turn%20back%20to%20the%20room.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20small%20motivations%20made%20Sakshi%E2%80%99s%20recovery%20easier.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn